<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Heinrich von Kaufungen, Hauptmann zu Totzau</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Freilassung und Herausgabe der Habe des Wilhelm von Castell, Sohn des Stefan von Castell, Bürger zu Nürnberg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_209" id="103v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_209_r1l20"><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von <expan>kauffung<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_209_r1l21">hauptman cʒu docʒaw </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_209_r1l22">Lieber her hauptman vns hat <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> Steffan von Caſtel </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_209_r1l23"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> . vvie Jr ſeinen Sun wılhelm von Caſtell </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_209_r1l24">gefangen vnd Jm etlıche ſein habe genomen habt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_209_r1l26"><expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> . daʒ Jr den <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>B<ex>urgers</ex></expan> Sun ledig 
<add><ab facs="#facs_209_r1l25">laſſen </ab></add> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_209_r1l27">Jm ſein habe wider <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_209_r1l28">Als etc Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_209" id="103v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von <expan>Kauffung<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                        hauptman czu Doczaw</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber her hauptman, uns hat <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> Steffan von
                        Castel, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, wie ir seinen sun Wilhelm von Castell
                        gefangen und im etliche sein habe genomen habt.
                            <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir den
                            <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan> sun ledig <add>lassen</add> und im sein habe
                        wider <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet, durch
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>. Als etc. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
